328
00:30:19,230 --> 00:30:21,530
Sang Hyeok has caused way too many problems.

329
00:30:21,530 --> 00:30:23,690
Look into the details.

330
00:30:23,690 --> 00:30:25,230
Yes, sir.

331
00:30:42,040 --> 00:30:44,370
