341
00:31:53,570 --> 00:31:56,470
Yes, I understand.

342
00:31:58,250 --> 00:31:59,790
Let's go back.

343
00:31:59,790 --> 00:32:01,320
Let's go back!

344
00:32:01,320 --> 00:32:03,880
Hey, get back!

345
00:32:03,880 --> 00:32:06,510
Shit, I said to get back!

346
00:32:54,080 --> 00:32:56,280
