safe, Detective?

354
00:33:25,540 --> 00:33:27,020
Yes.

355
00:33:34,590 --> 00:33:36,470
I'll defend you.

356
00:33:37,380 --> 00:33:41,170
This country isn't that sloppy.

357
00:34:01,010 --> 00:34:02,620
Grandmother...

358
00:34:04,130 --> 00:34:05,990
Cheong Ha...

359
00:34:16,610 --> 00:34:18,990
