490
00:46:46,980 --> 00:46:49,560
Your Honor!

491
00:46:49,560 --> 00:46:51,760
This sacred court was being controlled by their personal greed.

492
00:46:58,800 --> 00:47:00,560
That is all.

493
00:47:17,950 --> 00:47:19,610
With that...

494
00:47:20,750 --> 00:47:22,910
